name: woody-Juego multimedia
description:
Woody trata de un cowboy que ha sufrido una gran perdida, su sombrero a sido tomado por un grupo de pistoleros, y debe atacarles para recuperar su preciado sombrero vaquero.

The game is about a cowboy whose hat has been stolen by a group of bandits, and he must attack them to get his cowboy hat back.
